</style>

<!-- Global rules for dynamically-injected lightbox markup (no Astro scope id). -->
<style is:global>
  .cgb-root .lightbox-content img { display: block; max-width: 90vw; max-height: 80vh; object-fit: contain; }
  .cgb-root .lightbox-content img.qr-image {
    max-width: 320px;
    max-height: 320px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    display: block;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }
  .cgb-root .lightbox-content img.desktop-image {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--bg-raised);
    max-width: 80vw;
    image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast;
    image-rendering: crisp-edges;
  }
  .cgb-root .lightbox-multi { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; align-items: flex-start; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
  .cgb-root .lightbox-multi-item { flex: 1; min-width: 280px; max-width: 48%; text-align: center; }
  .cgb-root .lightbox-multi-item img { width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .cgb-root .lightbox-multi-label { margin-top: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary); letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; }
</style>

<script>
  (function () {
    'use strict';

    const IMG_BASE = '/images/guides/copilot-chat-basic/';
    const HEADER_OFFSET = 56 + 46; // sticky site header + guide sub-nav

    const root = document.querySelector('.cgb-root');
    if (!root) return;

    function resolveSrc(src) {
      return src && src.charAt(0) === '/' ? src : IMG_BASE + src;
    }

    /* ── Sample file downloads ── */
    const SAMPLE_FILES = {
      'Meeting-Notes-Category-Review.txt': `Category Review Meeting Notes - Kroger Salty Snacks
Date: [Today's Date]
Attendees: Sarah Chen (Kroger Category Manager), Mike Torres (Our Regional Sales Director), You

Key Discussion Points:
- Kroger wants to reduce SKU count in salty snacks by 10% to improve shelf productivity
- Our top 3 SKUs (Classic Sea Salt, BBQ Crunch, Ranch Dip Chips) are all performing above category average
- Two underperforming SKUs flagged: Spicy Lime (below 60% ACV threshold) and Sweet Chili (declining velocity)
- New product pitch: Protein Crisps line launching Q3 - buyer interested but wants margin data
- Q3 promotional calendar: Kroger requested a BOGO event for back-to-school (Aug weeks 2-3)
- Planogram reset scheduled for September - we may gain 2 additional facings if we cut the 2 underperformers
- Buyer mentioned competitor Brand X is pitching an exclusive flavor for Kroger
- Next review meeting tentatively scheduled for 8 weeks from now

Open Items:
- Need to send margin analysis for Protein Crisps line by Friday
- Confirm promotional funding for back-to-school BOGO
- Investigate Brand X exclusive flavor threat
- Schedule follow-up with broker to align on planogram submission`,
      'Q2-Territory-Metrics.csv': `Metric,Target,Actual,% to Goal
Revenue ($M),6.2,5.8,93.5%
Distribution Points (ACV %),78%,74%,94.9%
New Store Authorizations,45,52,115.6%
Void Closure Rate,85%,79%,92.9%
Promotional Compliance,90%,88%,97.8%
Shelf Condition Score,92,89,96.7%
Avg Store Visits/Week/Rep,22,20,90.9%
New SKU Placement Rate,70%,65%,92.9%`,
      'Q3-Trade-Promo-Proposal.txt': `Q3 TRADE PROMOTION PROPOSAL — KROGER SALTY SNACKS
Prepared by: [Your Name], Territory Sales Rep
Date: [Today's Date]

EXECUTIVE SUMMARY
Proposing a multi-tactic Q3 promotional program across Kroger's 2,700 stores to drive salty snack category growth and increase our brand's share from 18.2% to 20%+ by end of Q3.

PROMOTIONAL CALENDAR
Week 1-2 (July): Back-to-School BOGO on Classic Sea Salt and BBQ Crunch (8oz bags)
Week 5-6 (Aug): Temporary Price Reduction (TPR) $1.00 off Variety Packs (12ct)
Week 9-10 (Sep): New item introduction — Protein Crisps with in-store sampling at top 200 locations

PROJECTED ROI
- Total trade investment: $425,000
- Projected incremental revenue: $1.8M
- Projected lift: 22% during promotional weeks
- Estimated ROI: 4.2x

MERCHANDISING SUPPORT
- Secondary display (endcap) at 500 priority stores during BOGO period
- Shelf talkers for new Protein Crisps at all stores
- Digital circular feature for TPR weeks

RISKS & CONSIDERATIONS
- Inventory: Need 15% safety stock buffer for BOGO weeks based on prior year demand
- Timing: Back-to-school window overlaps with competitor Brand X's annual promo
- New item: Protein Crisps have no velocity history at Kroger

REQUESTED BUYER ACTIONS
1. Approve promotional calendar and funding allocation
2. Confirm endcap placement at 500 stores
3. Authorize new item setup for Protein Crisps (3 SKUs)`
    };

    window.downloadSample = function (filename) {
      const content = SAMPLE_FILES[filename];
      if (content == null) return;
      const mimeType = filename.endsWith('.csv') ? 'text/csv' : 'text/plain';
      const blob = new Blob([content], { type: mimeType });
      const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
      const a = document.createElement('a');
      a.href = url;
      a.download = filename;
      document.body.appendChild(a);
      a.click();
      document.body.removeChild(a);
      URL.revokeObjectURL(url);
    };

    /* ── Lightbox ── */
    function openOverlay(html, caption) {
      const overlay = document.getElementById('cgb-lightbox');
      document.getElementById('cgb-lightbox-body').innerHTML = html;
      document.getElementById('cgb-lightbox-caption').textContent = caption;
      overlay.classList.add('active');
      document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
    }

    window.openLightbox = function (src, caption, type) {
      const cls = type === 'desktop' ? 'desktop-image' : '';
      const html = '<img src="' + resolveSrc(src) + '" alt="' + caption + '" class="' + cls + '" style="display:block;max-width:90vw;max-height:80vh;object-fit:contain;">';
      openOverlay(html, caption);
    };

    window.openLightboxQR = function () {
      const html = '<img src="' + resolveSrc('copilot-mobile-qr.png') + '" alt="QR code to download M365 Copilot mobile app" class="qr-image">';
      openOverlay(html, 'Scan this QR code with your phone to download the Microsoft 365 Copilot mobile app');
    };

    window.openLightboxTeams = function () {
      const html =
        '<img src="' + resolveSrc('copilot-teams-open-and-closed.png') + '" alt="Teams with the Copilot Chat pane closed and open" style="display:block;max-width:90vw;max-height:80vh;object-fit:contain;">';
      openOverlay(html, 'Copilot Chat in Teams - click the Copilot icon in the left nav to open or collapse the sidebar');
    };

    function closeOverlay() {
      const overlay = document.getElementById('cgb-lightbox');
      overlay.classList.remove('active');
      document.body.style.overflow = '';
    }

    window.closeLightbox = function (e) {
      const content = document.getElementById('cgb-lightbox-content');
      if (e && e.target === content) return; // click inside content (not the close button)
      if (e && content && content.contains(e.target)) {
        if (e.target.classList.contains('lightbox-close') || (e.target.closest && e.target.closest('.lightbox-close'))) {
          closeOverlay();
        }
        return;
      }
      closeOverlay();
    };

    document.addEventListener('keydown', function (e) {
      if (e.key === 'Escape') {
        const overlay = document.getElementById('cgb-lightbox');
        if (overlay && overlay.classList.contains('active')) closeOverlay();
      }
    });

    /* ── Practice reveal ── */
    window.toggleReveal = function (btn) {
      const actions = btn.closest('.practice-actions') || btn.parentElement;
      const reveal = actions.querySelector('.practice-reveal');
      const isOpen = reveal.style.display !== 'none' && reveal.style.display !== '';
      reveal.style.display = isOpen ? 'none' : 'block';
      btn.textContent = isOpen ? 'See our suggestion ▼' : 'Hide suggestion ▲';
    };

    /* ── Evolve stepper ── */
    window.switchEvolve = function (level) {
      root.querySelectorAll('.evolve-tab').forEach(function (t) { t.classList.remove('active'); });
      root.querySelectorAll('.evolve-panel').forEach(function (p) { p.classList.remove('active'); });
      root.querySelector('.evolve-tab[data-level="' + level + '"]').classList.add('active');
      document.getElementById('evolve-' + level).classList.add('active');
    };

    /* ── Capability card expand/collapse ── */
    window.toggleCapability = function (header) {
      const card = header.closest('.capability-card');
      const detail = card.querySelector('.capability-detail');
      const inner = detail.querySelector('.capability-detail-inner');
      const wasOpen = card.classList.contains('open');
      card.classList.toggle('open');
      if (!wasOpen) {
        detail.style.maxHeight = inner.scrollHeight + 'px';
      } else {
        detail.style.maxHeight = '0';
        const rect = card.getBoundingClientRect();
        if (rect.top < 0) card.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
      }
    };

    // Inject collapse buttons into each capability detail.
    root.querySelectorAll('.capability-detail-inner').forEach(function (inner) {
      const btn = document.createElement('button');
      btn.className = 'collapse-btn';
      btn.type = 'button';
      btn.textContent = 'collapse';
      btn.setAttribute('aria-label', 'Collapse card');
      btn.addEventListener('click', function () {
        const card = inner.closest('.capability-card');
        window.toggleCapability(card.querySelector('.capability-header'));
      });
      inner.appendChild(btn);
    });

    /* ── Tabs ── */
    window.switchTab = function (btn, panelId) {
      root.querySelectorAll('.tab-btn').forEach(function (b) { b.classList.remove('active'); b.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'false'); });
      root.querySelectorAll('.tab-panel').forEach(function (p) { p.classList.remove('active'); });
      btn.classList.add('active');
      btn.setAttribute('aria-selected', 'true');
      const panel = document.getElementById(panelId);
      panel.classList.add('active');
      panel.querySelectorAll('.fade-in:not(.visible)').forEach(function (el) { fadeObserver.observe(el); });
    };

    /* ── Copy prompt ── */
    window.copyPrompt = function (el) {
      const clone = el.cloneNode(true);
      clone.querySelectorAll('.copy-hint').forEach(function (n) { n.remove(); });
      const text = clone.innerText.trim();
      const hint = el.querySelector('.copy-hint');
      function done() {
        showToast('Copied!');
        if (hint) { hint.textContent = 'Copied'; setTimeout(function () { hint.textContent = 'Click to copy'; }, 1500); }
      }
      if (navigator.clipboard && navigator.clipboard.writeText) {
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(done).catch(fallback);
      } else {
        fallback();
      }
      function fallback() {
        const ta = document.createElement('textarea');
        ta.value = text;
        ta.style.position = 'fixed';
        ta.style.opacity = '0';
        document.body.appendChild(ta);
        ta.select();
        try { document.execCommand('copy'); } catch (err) { /* no-op */ }
        document.body.removeChild(ta);
        done();
      }
    };

    /* ── Toast ── */
    let toastTimer;
    function showToast(msg) {
      const t = document.getElementById('cgb-toast');
      t.textContent = msg;
      t.classList.add('show');
      clearTimeout(toastTimer);
      toastTimer = setTimeout(function () { t.classList.remove('show'); }, 2000);
    }

    /* ── Checklist ── */
    const STORAGE_KEY = 'copilot-guide-checklist';
    let checks = [];
    try { checks = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(STORAGE_KEY) || '[]'); } catch (e) { checks = []; }
    if (!Array.isArray(checks) || checks.length !== 10) checks = new Array(10).fill(false);

    function renderChecklist() {
      const items = root.querySelectorAll('.checklist-item');
      let done = 0;
      items.forEach(function (item, i) {
        const cb = item.querySelector('.checklist-checkbox');
        if (checks[i]) {
          cb.classList.add('checked');
          cb.setAttribute('aria-checked', 'true');
          item.classList.add('completed');
          done++;
        } else {
          cb.classList.remove('checked');
          cb.setAttribute('aria-checked', 'false');
          item.classList.remove('completed');
        }
      });
      document.getElementById('cgb-progress-count').textContent = done;
      document.getElementById('cgb-progress-bar').style.width = (done / 10 * 100) + '%';
      document.getElementById('cgb-congrats-msg').classList.toggle('visible', done === 10);
    }

    window.toggleCheck = function (cb) {
      const item = cb.closest('.checklist-item');
      const idx = parseInt(item.getAttribute('data-check'), 10);
      checks[idx] = !checks[idx];
      try { localStorage.setItem(STORAGE_KEY, JSON.stringify(checks)); } catch (e) { /* no-op */ }
      cb.style.transform = 'scale(1.2)';
      setTimeout(function () { cb.style.transform = ''; }, 200);
      renderChecklist();
    };

    renderChecklist();

    /* ── Fade-in on scroll ── */
    const fadeObserver = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
      entries.forEach(function (entry) {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          const idx = Array.from(root.querySelectorAll('.fade-in:not(.visible)')).indexOf(entry.target);
          const delay = Math.max(0, idx) * 60;
          setTimeout(function () { entry.target.classList.add('visible'); }, Math.min(delay, 300));
          fadeObserver.unobserve(entry.target);
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.1 });
    root.querySelectorAll('.fade-in').forEach(function (el) { fadeObserver.observe(el); });

    /* ── Active sub-nav link ── */
    const sections = root.querySelectorAll('section[id]');
    const navLinks = root.querySelectorAll('.cgb-subnav-links a');
    const navObserver = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
      entries.forEach(function (entry) {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          const id = entry.target.getAttribute('id');
          navLinks.forEach(function (link) {
            link.classList.toggle('active', link.getAttribute('href') === '#' + id);
          });
        }
      });
    }, { rootMargin: '-120px 0px -55% 0px', threshold: 0 });
    sections.forEach(function (s) { navObserver.observe(s); });

    /* ── Smooth scroll for in-page anchors (offset for sticky chrome) ── */
    root.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(function (a) {
      a.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
        const id = a.getAttribute('href').slice(1);
        if (!id) return;
        const target = document.getElementById(id);
        if (!target) return;
        e.preventDefault();
        const y = target.getBoundingClientRect().top + window.scrollY - HEADER_OFFSET;
        window.scrollTo({ top: y, behavior: 'smooth' });
      });
    });

    /* ── Scroll progress & back to top ── */
    const progressBar = document.getElementById('cgb-scroll-progress');
    const backToTop = document.getElementById('cgb-back-to-top');
    if (backToTop) backToTop.addEventListener('click', function () { window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' }); });
    window.addEventListener('scroll', function () {
      const scrollTop = window.scrollY || document.documentElement.scrollTop;
      const docHeight = document.documentElement.scrollHeight - document.documentElement.clientHeight;
      const scrollPercent = docHeight > 0 ? (scrollTop / docHeight) * 100 : 0;
      if (progressBar) progressBar.style.width = scrollPercent + '%';
      if (backToTop) backToTop.classList.toggle('visible', scrollTop > 400);
    }, { passive: true });
  })();
</script>
